He's the most-subscribed YouTuber in the world.

1248
00:43:17,861 --> 00:43:19,200
Right.

1249
00:43:19,201 --> 00:43:20,930
The team's name is MrBeast,

1250
00:43:20,931 --> 00:43:22,430
and the character I'm dubbing...

1251
