is Jimmy Donaldson, the leader.

1252
00:43:25,501 --> 00:43:26,770
- There are many members. - Yes.

1253
00:43:26,771 --> 00:43:28,470
There are different voice actors for every member?

1254
00:43:28,471 --> 00:43:30,341
- Are there different voice actors? - Right.

1255
00:43:30,511 --> 00:43:32,910
Does he work with all of you?

1256
00:43:32,911 --> 00:43:34,110
- Yes. - He hires them.

1257
00:43:34,111 --> 00:43:35,111
All around the world.

1258
00:43:35,111 --> 00:43:36,111
There's a history about this.

1259
00:43:36,112 --> 00:43:37,780
You'll know when you hear it.

1260
00:43:37,781 --> 00:43:39,281
- It's a different tone. - Right.

1261
00:43:39,481 --> 00:43:41,751
"Today, I'll introduce Men on a Mission to you."

1262
00:43:42,321 --> 00:43:43,890
"To those who watch this show until the end,"

1263
00:43:43,891 --> 00:43:45,521
"Ho Dong will give one million dollars."

1264
00:43:45,861 --> 00:43:47,730
- I think I've heard this. - Right.

1265
00:43:47,731 --> 00:43:48,790
They give you money.

1266
00:43:48,791 --> 00:43:49,930
They really give you money.

1267
00:43:49,931 --> 00:43:51,000
This is how I started dubbing it.

1268
00:43:51,001 --> 00:43:53,031
The channel's name is "MrBeast."

1269
00:43:53,161 --> 00:43:54,770
When "Squid Game" was a trend,

1270
00:43:54,771 --> 00:43:56,800
- he built the "Squid Game" set... - Right.

1271
00:43:56,801 --> 00:43:58,570
