1272
00:43:58,571 --> 00:44:00,001
He became famous in Korea.

1273
00:44:00,101 --> 00:44:03,811
I think that's when he realized he had many Korean fans.

1274
00:44:04,111 --> 00:44:06,441
So there was an audition for voice actors.

1275
00:44:06,481 --> 00:44:08,911
- You went there. - It was at an ordinary studio.

1276
00:44:09,011 --> 00:44:11,420
About 5 or 7 people auditioned...

1277
00:44:11,421 --> 00:44:13,420
and I was accepted. I started recording,

1278
00:44:13,421 --> 00:44:14,920
and what I'm grateful about is that I've been recording it...

1279
00:44:14,921 --> 00:44:16,421
