1282
00:44:20,931 --> 00:44:22,831
After 13 episodes, we resume after several months.

1283
00:44:23,191 --> 00:44:26,060
But there's a recording every week for "MrBeast."

1284
00:44:26,061 --> 00:44:27,600
Right. They upload a video every week.

1285
00:44:27,601 --> 00:44:29,531
They asked me to record 100 videos in a month.

1286
00:44:29,601 --> 00:44:31,440
(She's shocked.)

1287
00:44:31,441 --> 00:44:34,671
I recorded those in 50 hours within the month...

1288
00:44:34,871 --> 00:44:36,411
