1289
00:44:36,611 --> 00:44:38,840
I recorded three times a day.

1290
00:44:38,841 --> 00:44:41,081
I recorded from 9am to 12pm.

1291
00:44:41,181 --> 00:44:43,510
Then I had lunch and went for another schedule.

1292
00:44:43,511 --> 00:44:45,251
Then I recorded from 6pm to 9pm.

1293
00:44:45,581 --> 00:44:48,120
I went to bed at night but I wanted to do more.

1294
00:44:48,121 --> 00:44:49,720
My throat hurts just from listening to that.

1295
00:44:49,721 --> 00:44:51,921
So I went there again and recorded from 2am to 5am.

1296
00:44:52,261 --> 00:44:53,860
- How is the pay? - It's...

1297
00:44:53,861 --> 00:44:55,060
