1298
00:44:55,061 --> 00:44:56,960
- The payment. - You would have done it...

1299
00:44:56,961 --> 00:44:58,530
- with passion because it was fine. - Right.

1300
00:44:58,531 --> 00:44:59,600
I guess they paid a lot.

1301
00:44:59,601 --> 00:45:01,330
- Jimmy... - Jimmy would pay you a lot.

1302
00:45:01,331 --> 00:45:03,800
