1303
00:45:03,801 --> 00:45:05,170
- Right. - So you'd think...

1304
00:45:05,171 --> 00:45:06,800
the voice actors would be paid a lot too.

1305
00:45:06,801 --> 00:45:08,671
The payment for an episode isn't several thousand dollars.

1306
00:45:08,941 --> 00:45:11,741
But I've worked on more than 700 episodes.

1307
00:45:12,011 --> 00:45:13,180
- Really? - So,

1308
00:45:13,181 --> 00:45:15,980
I didn't get paid so much as if I won the lottery,

1309
00:45:15,981 --> 00:45:18,620
but I received enough payment for my efforts.

1310
00:45:18,621 --> 00:45:20,080
They keep giving you work.

1311
00:45:20,081 --> 00:45:21,350
- I'm so thankful. - Jimmy.

1312
00:45:21,351 --> 00:45:23,290
I'm also thankful because it's a character...

1313
00:45:23,291 --> 00:45:24,490
- who everyone knows. - Right.

1314
00:45:24,491 --> 00:45:25,491
Yes.

1315
00:45:25,492 --> 00:45:28,031
