1366
00:47:06,291 --> 00:47:09,360
To co-host the show live.

1367
00:47:09,361 --> 00:47:11,000
I said I wouldn't do it.

1368
00:47:11,001 --> 00:47:12,001
Why?

1369
00:47:12,331 --> 00:47:14,770
- How would I do that? - Between family members...

1370
