"We have Mr. Ahn Ji Hwan, the voice actor, as a guest."

1371
00:47:18,941 --> 00:47:20,900
When my daughter called me "Mr. Ahn Ji Hwan,"

1372
00:47:20,901 --> 00:47:23,170
- Right. - it didn't feel right...

1373
00:47:23,171 --> 00:47:24,910
