1374
00:47:24,911 --> 00:47:26,840
You also feel anxious.

1375
00:47:26,841 --> 00:47:28,611
You fought with your daughter there.

1376
00:47:28,881 --> 00:47:30,080
We ended up fighting.

1377
00:47:30,081 --> 00:47:32,280
We ended up fighting. When we fight...

1378
00:47:32,281 --> 00:47:33,820
- During the show? - It's similar to when we dub.

1379
