1385
00:47:45,031 --> 00:47:46,530
"You can't say that on a show."

1386
00:47:46,531 --> 00:47:48,000
"Why did you say ilkssib?"

1387
00:47:48,001 --> 00:47:49,871
- "That's because you're old." - "The music ended."

1388
00:47:50,831 --> 00:47:52,001
"Read the story."

1389
00:47:52,501 --> 00:47:54,200
This is how it goes.

1390
00:47:54,201 --> 00:47:55,940
It became very difficult.

1391
00:47:55,941 --> 00:47:57,910
- Seriously. - Didn't the listeners like that?

1392
00:47:57,911 --> 00:48:01,010
We've been hosting it for two years now,

1393
00:48:01,011 --> 00:48:05,020
