1406
00:48:32,811 --> 00:48:34,310
People look at me.

1407
00:48:34,311 --> 00:48:35,580
She likes pulling pranks.

1408
00:48:35,581 --> 00:48:37,050
- Seriously. - She's mischievous.

1409
00:48:37,051 --> 00:48:38,650
She calls me "Honey." Also,

1410
