1431
00:49:20,921 --> 00:49:22,561
Why? I'm her dad!

1432
00:49:24,461 --> 00:49:26,400
- "I'm her dad." - He is her dad.

1433
00:49:26,401 --> 00:49:27,930
- He's her dad. - He's her dad!

1434
00:49:27,931 --> 00:49:29,770
- I'm her dad. - Next,

